creator: TOTERapp LLC
descriptionHtml:
MAKE GREAT MONEY WITH YOUR BIKE OR CAR
Have a bike or car and got some free time? Why not make some money? With TOTERS, you can set your schedule in advance and generate money from your vehicle
Use Your Own Phone. The app is free to download on your own Android device (must be 2013 or newer).

HOW DO I GET STARTED?
Sign up to deliver www.totersapp.com/shopper/ and start your application.
Send us your ID and vehicle documents, then download this app onto your phone.
Once you are registered and approved, someone will contact you to set up your schedule. You can then start delivering and earn money.

MAKE GREAT MONEY WITH YOUR BIKE OR CAR
Have a bike or car and got some free time? Why not make some money? With TOTERS, you can set your schedule in advance and generate money from your vehicle
Use Your Own Phone. The app is free to download on your own Android device (must be 2013 or newer).

HOW DO I GET STARTED?
Sign up to deliver www.totersapp.com/shopper/ and start your application.
Send us your ID and vehicle documents, then download this app onto your phone.
Once you are registered and approved, someone will contact you to set up your schedule. You can then start delivering and earn money.
